It is recommended to create a small batch of tablets first to test profitability before committing to a larger number.

Players can expect to create 1100-1150 teleport tablets per hour with an inventory of 26 clay tablets, banking at the [[Lunar Isle bank]], and auto-creating tablets at the [[Lectern (Lunar)]].

All calculations on this page assume the player uses the appropriate [[Staves|Staff]].

